# sycom-portal – IT Support Portal

## O projekte
Fullstack IT support portal pre Sycom s.r.o.
- Produkcia: /opt/sycom-portal (PM2 id:0, port 3000, domena portal.sycom.sk)
- Staging:   /opt/sycom-portal-staging (PM2 id:2, port 3001)
- Staging je testovaci server pred nasadenim na produkciu

## Tech stack
- Framework: Next.js 14 (App Router)
- Databaza: MariaDB 10.6+ cez Prisma ORM
- Auth: NextAuth (JWT session, role-based: ADMIN / AGENT / CLIENT)
- UI: Tailwind CSS, Recharts, React Hook Form, Zod
- Email: nodemailer, imapflow, mailparser
- PDF: jsPDF, html2canvas
- Runtime: PM2 cluster mode, Nginx reverse proxy

## Struktura projektu
src/app/api/
  auth/        NextAuth
  tickets/     CRUD tiketov
  users/       sprava pouzivatelov
  kb/          znalostna baza
  reports/     statistiky

src/app/(auth)/login/     prihlasovacia stranka
src/app/(client)/         klientska cast
  dashboard/
  tickets/
  kb/
src/app/(admin)/admin/    admin sekcia
  users/
  teams/
  reports/

src/lib/
  prisma.ts    DB klient
  auth.ts      NextAuth konfiguracia
  email.ts     emailove notifikacie
  utils.ts     pomocne funkcie

prisma/
  schema.prisma   databazova schema
  seed.ts         testovacie data

## Dolezite subory
- .env / .env.example    environment premenne
- ecosystem.config.js    PM2 konfiguracia
- sycom-portal.nginx     Nginx konfiguracia
- deploy.sh              deploy skript

## Bezpecnost
- Hesla: bcrypt (cost factor 12)
- Sessions: JWT cez NextAuth
- RBAC: ADMIN / AGENT / CLIENT role
- Validacia: Zod
- DB: Prisma ORM (SQL injection ochrana)
- HTTPS + HSTS cez Nginx

